    "body": "…preview\r\n\r\nProblem:\r\nmatchadd() highlights go to char_attr_pri, while inccommand preview goes to char_attr_base. char_attr_pri always wins.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nput matches below SEARCH_HL_PRIORITY in char_attr_base instead.\r\n\r\nFix #37848 \r\n",
